formThreeAList.alloteeName: JIVAN JYOT CO OP HOS SOC

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The certificate is issued on the basis of unaudited books of accounts and reasonable informations available with us.
2. The project stands completed on 16-03-2019, however, inadvertantly due to the reason provided in writing before the Authorities, this fresh opportunities for filing the QE is initiated and filed herewith.
3. The promoter maintains 4 bank accounts other than the account declared in the RERA Registration and the same belonged to the partner of the promoter and the promoters have not applied for BCR which the authorities take a note.
4. The RERA Bank Details provided in the Certificate are pertaining to an exclusive account maintained by the Promoter with the primary lender bank and the same has been taken into consideration. The other bank transactions are not mentioned and thus amount withdrawn from Designated accounts against the previous certificates is not verifiable and for the purpose of brewity the entire receipts from booked inventory have been mentioned.
5. There are unreconciled differences in amount received from booked inventory as per Annexure 3A of RERA and as per books and the management has not provided reconciliation for the same. Further, we are not in the position to verify the ATS and date of sale documents and thus we dont verify the date of agreement for the units booked.
